Here's a detailed **API documentation** for your **Contract Management Microservice**.

---

## üìù **Base URL**
```
http://localhost:8080
```

---

## üìå **1. Clients API**
### ‚û§ **Create a Client**
```http
POST /clients
```
**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "clientName": "ABC Corp",
  "businessType": "IT Services"
}
```

‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "clientId": 1,
  "clientName": "ABC Corp",
  "businessType": "IT Services"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get All Clients**
```http
GET /clients
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
[
  {
    "clientId": 1,
    "clientName": "ABC Corp",
    "businessType": "IT Services"
  },
  {
    "clientId": 2,
    "clientName": "XYZ Ltd",
    "businessType": "Finance"
  }
]
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get a Client by ID**
```http
GET /clients/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "clientId": 1,
  "clientName": "ABC Corp",
  "businessType": "IT Services"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Update a Client**
```http
PUT /clients/{id}
```
**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "clientName": "ABC Corporation",
  "businessType": "Tech"
}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "clientId": 1,
  "clientName": "ABC Corporation",
  "businessType": "Tech"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Delete a Client**
```http
DELETE /clients/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**  
```
204 No Content
```

---

## üìå **2. Contracts API**
### ‚û§ **Create a Contract**
```http
POST /contracts
```
**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "client": { "clientId": 1 },
  "contractType": "Permanent"
}
```

‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "contractId": 1,
  "client": {
    "clientId": 1,
    "clientName": "ABC Corp"
  },
  "contractType": "Permanent",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00",
  "updatedAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get All Contracts**
```http
GET /contracts
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
[
  {
    "contractId": 1,
    "client": {
      "clientId": 1,
      "clientName": "ABC Corp"
    },
    "contractType": "Permanent",
    "createdAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00",
    "updatedAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00"
  }
]
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get a Contract by ID**
```http
GET /contracts/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "contractId": 1,
  "client": {
    "clientId": 1,
    "clientName": "ABC Corp"
  },
  "contractType": "Permanent",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00",
  "updatedAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Update a Contract**
```http
PUT /contracts/{id}
```
**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "contractType": "Routing"
}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "contractId": 1,
  "client": {
    "clientId": 1,
    "clientName": "ABC Corp"
  },
  "contractType": "Routing",
  "createdAt": "2024-02-01T10:30:00",
  "updatedAt": "2024-02-02T11:45:00"
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Delete a Contract**
```http
DELETE /contracts/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**  
```
204 No Content
```

