## üìå **3. Permanent Contracts API**
### ‚û§ **Create a Permanent Contract**
```http
POST /permanent-contracts
```
**Request Body:**
```json
{
  "contract": { "contractId": 1 },
  "permanentPercentage": 15.50
}
```

‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "permanentId": 1,
  "contract": {
    "contractId": 1,
    "contractType": "Permanent"
  },
  "permanentPercentage": 15.50
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get All Permanent Contracts**
```http
GET /permanent-contracts
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
[
  {
    "permanentId": 1,
    "contract": {
      "contractId": 1,
      "contractType": "Permanent"
    },
    "permanentPercentage": 15.50
  }
]
```

---

### ‚û§ **Get a Permanent Contract by ID**
```http
GET /permanent-contracts/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**
```json
{
  "permanentId": 1,
  "contract": {
    "contractId": 1,
    "contractType": "Permanent"
  },
  "permanentPercentage": 15.50
}
```

---

### ‚û§ **Delete a Permanent Contract**
```http
DELETE /permanent-contracts/{id}
```
‚úÖ **Response:**  
```
204 No Content
```

